title: Bells
description:
This app will take you to the world of sounds of church bells. You will be able to compose their own music peals of 12 high-quality sounds of old church bells. For centuries, we know that the sounds of the bells have miraculous powers. Bell zones heals body and soul. 

Using sounds of bells easy for anyone. You can listen to some sounds, holding your finger on the screen or composes interesting melodies using multitouch on your phone. The application is optimized for maximum volume and listening comfort. The sounds of bells is music spirit and everyone will find their own rhythm, its melody
